<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8">4.诸人需于道观穿墙破壁、凿井取土时，要报告职管处，寻求谕文，说明原因，若违律，属自行为之，按照诸人于寺观住宿法判断(51)。</td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
<tr>
<td class="text8"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<table width="438" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
